{"tid":1524775,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"青衣超級車務控制中心","createTime":"2019-08-31T18:10:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T17:39:39.000Z","uid":285467,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d17c58633befb7aae5f5cd3625f907841a3739bf","tid":1524775,"uid":285467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:10:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">青衣超級車務控制中心</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n為香港港鐵最主要的車務控制中心，位於港鐵青衣站<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">U5層</span></strong>位於青衣站那個位置? 青衣站C出口，即係珀麗灣巴士站對出有一部lift可以上到<br />\n<br />\n於1998年啟用。統一管理港鐵所有重型鐵路綫（即<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">荃灣綫、觀塘綫、港島綫、將軍澳綫、東鐵綫、西鐵綫、馬鞍山綫、東涌綫、機場快綫、迪士尼綫及南港島綫</span></strong>）的運作。超級車務控制中心面積達700平方米（約7500平方英尺），採用劇院式設計，控制員、技術員等坐於「後座」，前排控制台則是行車控制主任座位，設有一個長120米、由99個超高清大型投射屏幕組織而成的屏幕牆，可以同時顯示各路線列車於實際時間的所在位置，月台、列車車廂、列車駕駛室閉路電視畫面及各車站的環境數據等；由約170名職員負責，24小時全天候運作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n位於青衣站那個位置? 青衣站C出口，即係珀麗灣巴士站對出有一部lift可以上到"},{"pid":"5fe6b3f78c22051635d994df15c50476f0184570","tid":1524775,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:11:27.000Z","msg":"黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f3fcb26396a6f2d9f4f8a7965fad7a37f33531","tid":1524775,"uid":149427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:12:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b4524961b3708575a488f41c394fdd254436c3","tid":1524775,"uid":149427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:12:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f8ef5b9315ef024e53e